<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="V" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Vasty" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Vasty,</orth> vast, boundless: <cit><quote>the v. wilds of wide Arabia,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.7.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 7, 41</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I can call spirits from the v. deep,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.52" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 1, 52</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>can this cockpit hold the v. fields of France?</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.52" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 1, 52</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to v. Tartar,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.2.123" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 123</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>for whom this hungry war opens his v. jaws,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.105" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 105</bibl></cit>.
<pb n="1311" />
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>